Author: snakepack
Text: (tw numbers)  hey!!!!! we r kinda in the same boat!! im transmasc 5'0"- i'm plateau-ing at 94 lbs (sw 98.5 lbs), though a few days ago i weighed myself (right after i woke up) & i was 91, but the next day i was somehow back at 94? :/ i've been bouncing between 94 and 94.5 for roughly a year,, idk how to lose any more, & my bmi is BARELY underweight tbh. kinda annoying lol
